OL,6,FA man hired as a gardener by an
OL,7,Felderly couple returned with his
OL,8,Fbrother weeks later to carry out a
OL,9,F"barbaric" robbery.
OL,11,FJohn Gibbons and his brother, Mark,
OL,12,Fattacked the victims in their rural
OL,13,Fhome in Malton, North Yorkshire,
OL,14,Frepeatedly punching them and
OL,15,Fthreatening to mutilate the woman with
OL,16,Fa cheese grater, York Crown Court
OL,17,Fheard.
