OL,3,CGardener-turned-robber threatened to
OL,4,Cmutilate elderly woman
OL,6,FThe court was told John Gibbons had
OL,7,Fbeen hired by the couple two months
OL,8,Fearlier after they responded to an
OL,9,Fadvertisement for a gardener.
OL,11,FThey paid him a #3,500 bill to get rid
OL,12,Fof him after finding his behaviour
OL,13,F"strange", police said.
OL,15,FTwo months later the couple were
OL,16,Fwatching television when the brothers
OL,17,Fsmashed through their front door
OL,18,Fwearing balaclavas and demanding money.
