OL,3,CGardener-turned-robber threatened to
OL,4,Cmutilate elderly woman
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police said the pair
OL,7,Fspent half an hour beating the
OL,8,Fvictims. They punched both in the
OL,9,Fhead, pinned the man to the floor by
OL,10,Fhis neck and threatened to use
OL,11,Fscissors and a cheese grater on the
OL,12,Fwoman's face.
OL,14,FBoth suffered severe bruising and cuts
OL,15,Ffollowing the attack.
OL,17,FThe Gibbons brothers ransacked the
OL,18,Fhouse, filling a carrier bag with
OL,19,Fjewellery, cash and the couple's
OL,20,Fphones.
