OL,3,CGardener-turned-robber threatened to
OL,4,Cmutilate elderly woman
OL,6,FAfter they left, the victims called
OL,7,F999. Detectives tracked down the pair
OL,8,Fin West Yorkshire and both were
OL,9,Farrested within 36 hours of the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FDet Cons Nicholas Burton said the fact
OL,13,FMark Gibbons was still wearing the
OL,14,Fstolen personalised ring and chain
OL,15,Fwhich belonged to a deceased member of
OL,16,Fthe victims' family "speaks volumes
OL,17,Fabout him."
OL,19,FHe added: "To call this attack
OL,20,Fhorrific is an understatement.
