OL,3,CGardener-turned-robber threatened to
OL,4,Cmutilate elderly woman
OL,6,F"The Gibbons used barbaric levels of
OL,7,Faggression against a totally innocent
OL,8,Fcouple."
OL,10,FDet Cons Burton said attacks of this
OL,11,Fnature are "extremely rare" in North
OL,12,FYorkshire but was a "terrifying
OL,13,Fordeal" for the victims.
OL,15,F"After all they've been subjected to,
OL,16,Ftheir courage to the very end has been
OL,17,Fadmirable. It has helped convict two
OL,18,Fvery violent defendants who were
OL,19,Fdescribed in court as cowardly thugs
OL,20,Fand are now starting long prison
OL,21,Fsentences."
