OL,6,FMark Gibbons, 44, of Heckmondwike,
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire, pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Frobbery and was sentenced to 13 years
OL,9,Fand nine months in prison.
OL,11,FJohn Gibbons, 38, and also of
OL,12,FHeckmondwike, was jailed for nine-and-
OL,13,Fa-half years after pleading not guilty
OL,14,Fbut being found guilty by a jury.
